'''梅健華'''（{{lang-en|Kin Wah Moy}}，{{bd|1966年||df=y}}<ref name="CommonWealth Magazine"/>），[[美國|美國]][[外交官|外交官]]，生於[[英屬香港|英屬香港]]，籍貫[[廣東省|廣東省]][[台山市|台山市]]，是第三代[[華裔美國人|華裔美國人]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.waou.com.mo/news_b/shownews.php?lang=cn&id=557 |publisher=[[新華澳報|新華澳報]] |author=富權 |title=華府任命梅健華是為應對臺北政壇巨變？ |date=2015-05-10 |accessdate=2018-12-14 |archive-date=2018-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214091152/http://www.waou.com.mo/news_b/shownews.php?lang=cn&id=557 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，為資深職業外交官，[[外交官銜|外交官銜]]為[[公使|公使]]<ref name="公使">{{Cite web |title=PN1419 — Foreign Service, 116th Congress (2019-2020) |url=https://www.congress.gov/nomination/116th-congress/1419/all-info |publisher=[[美國國會|United States Congress]] |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200426045906/https://www.congress.gov/nomination/116th-congress/1419/all-info |date=2020-01-09 |archivedate=2020-04-26 |access-date=2020-02-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。梅健華自2021年6月起就任[[美國國務院東亞暨太平洋事務局|國務院東亞太平洋局]]首席副助卿<ref name="國務院亞太局">{{citation |url=https://www.state.gov/biographies/kin-w-moy/ |archive-url=https://archive.today/20210617110450/https://www.state.gov/biographies/kin-w-moy/ |url-status=no |archive-date=2021-06-17 |publisher={{lang|en|[[United_States_Department_of_State|United States Department of State]]}} |script-title=en:Kin W. Moy, Principal Deputy Assistant Secretary, Bureau of East Asian and Pacific Affairs |accessdate=2021-06-17 }}</ref>，早前曾任{{Link-en|美國國務院情報研究局|Bureau of Intelligence and Research}}代理助卿<ref name="國務院情研局">{{Cite web  |script-title=en: Kin Moy  - Acting Assistant Secretary - Bureau of Intelligence and Research  |url=https://www.state.gov/biographies/kin-moy/  |publisher={{lang|en|[[United_States_Department_of_State|United States Department of State]]}}  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319003113/https://www.state.gov/biographies/kin-moy/  |archivedate=2021-03-19  |access-date=2021-03-26  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>、首席副助卿<ref name="INR">{{citation |url=https://www.state.gov/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Org-Directory.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200501185613/https://www.state.gov/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Org-Directory.pdf |archive-date=2020-05-01 |date=2020-04-28 |publisher=[[United_States_Department_of_State|United States Department of State]] |title=Telephone Directory - Organizational Directory |page=OD-41 |access-date=2020-05-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2015年至2018年間則曾擔任[[美國在台協會|美國在台協會]]臺北辦事處處長，是該職首位華裔出身者。梅氏畢業於[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞大學]]和[[明尼苏达大学|明尼蘇達大學]]，並可通[[華語|華語]]和[[粵語|粵語]]<ref name="國務院亞太局"/>。具有在[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]及數座[[美國駐外機構列表|駐外使領館]]服職的經驗，在外交單位資歷長達二十多年，尤其嫻熟亞太地區事務。

